ğŸ“˜ Exam Seating Arrangement System

A Full-Stack Web Application




ğŸ“Œ Project Overview

The Exam Seating Arrangement System is a full-stack web application designed to digitally manage exams, users, seating plans, and seating visibility for students, teachers, and administrators.

It eliminates manual seating allocation and allows:

Admins to manage exams & permissions

Teachers to upload seating CSV files

Students to securely view their seating arrangement

The project follows role-based access control, ensuring each user only sees what they are allowed to.





ğŸ§± Technology Stack
ğŸ”¹ Frontend

