ğŸ”¹ Backend

Node.js

Express.js

MongoDB (Mongoose ORM)

JWT Authentication

Multer (File uploads)

PapaParse (CSV parsing)

ğŸ”¹ Database

MongoDB Atlas / Local MongoDB

Collections for users, exams, uploads, seating plans, requests





