ğŸ” Authentication & Security

JWT-based authentication

Tokens stored in localStorage

Automatic logout on token expiry

Role-based route protection using ProtectedRoute

Backend role guards using middleware




ğŸ“Š Seating Arrangement Flow (Important)

Teacher uploads seating CSV for an exam

File is stored in:

Database (uploads collection)

File system (/backend/uploads)

Students click â€œView Seatingâ€

CSV is:

Read from backend

Parsed using PapaParse

Displayed as a table on the frontend




âš ï¸ No seating grid logic is used for students â€” CSV is shown directly as requested.

