ğŸ”„ API Communication

Frontend â†’ Backend via Axios

Base URL:

http://localhost:5000/api


JWT token automatically attached using Axios interceptors

Unauthorized access redirects user to login




ğŸ“„ CSV Format (Seating Upload)

Example CSV structure:

rollNumber,seat,row,col
CS101,R1-C1,1,1
CS102,R1-C2,1,2


Other column names are also supported as long as rollNumber exists.





